  m_Name: FusePlacement
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  header: Fuse
  description: In this level, you have a fuse to ignite barrels from a distance.
    If you're near a barrel, press F to start placing the fuse, then hold F to lay
    it down. The fuse has a limit, but you can connect more fuses to make it longer.
    Use it wisely!
